FoodicsCRM API Endpoints

Restaurant Management

- Add Foodics Restaurant
  Method: POST
  Endpoint: /api/CRM/v{version}/FoodicsCRM/AddFoodicsRestaurant

- Get Single Restaurant
  Method: GET
  Endpoint: /api/CRM/v{version}/FoodicsCRM/GetSingleRestaurant/{restaurantId}

- Get Restaurant Main Groups Dropdown
  Method: GET
  Endpoint: /api/CRM/v{version}/FoodicsCRM/GetRestaurantMainGroupsDropDown/{restaurantId}

- Update Foodics Restaurant
  Method: PUT
  Endpoint: /api/CRM/v{version}/FoodicsCRM/UpdateFoodicsRestaurant

- Delete Foodics Restaurant
  Method: DELETE
  Endpoint: /api/CRM/v{version}/FoodicsCRM/DeleteFoodicsRestaurant/{Id}

- Delete Menu Group Restaurant
  Method: DELETE
  Endpoint: /api/CRM/v{version}/FoodicsCRM/DeleteMenuGroupRestaurant/{Id}

- Upload Foodics Restaurant Images
  Method: POST
  Endpoint: /api/CRM/v{version}/FoodicsCRM/UploadFoodicsRestaurantImages

- Get Foodics Restaurant Details
  Method: GET
  Endpoint: /api/CRM/v{version}/FoodicsCRM/GetFoodicsRestaurantDetails/{FoodicsRestaurantId}

- Get Foodics Restaurant By Menu Types
  Method: GET
  Endpoint: /api/CRM/v{version}/FoodicsCRM/GetFoodicsRestauranByMenuTypes

- Get Menu Type Dropdown List
  Method: GET
  Endpoint: /api/CRM/v{version}/FoodicsCRM/GetMenuTypeDropDownlist

- Get Foodics Management System Dropdown List
  Method: GET
  Endpoint: /api/CRM/v{version}/FoodicsCRM/GetFoodicsManagementSystemDropDownlist

- Get All Restaurants by Location
  Method: GET
  Endpoint: /api/CRM/v{version}/FoodicsCRM/GetAllRestaurant/{locationId}

- Get All Restaurants Dropdown by Location
  Method: GET
  Endpoint: /api/CRM/v{version}/FoodicsCRM/GetAllRestaurantDropDown/{locationId}

